                <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 italic">"Tadpole handles the volume, you handle the value."</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-8 order-1 md:order-2">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight leading-tight">Shared <br/><span class="text-emerald-500">Prosperity</span></h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-lg">
              We build for the people who build the business. Transition from manual workflows to overseeing a portfolio of AI specialists.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="p-6 glass-surface rounded-2xl flex gap-6 items-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-emerald-500/30 flex items-center justify-center text-xl bg-emerald-500/5">‚ö°</div>
                <div class="flex-1">
