                  <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">One employee can now manage a month's worth of documentation in an afternoon.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6 glass-surface rounded-2xl flex gap-6 items-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-emerald-500/30 flex items-center justify-center text-xl bg-emerald-500/5">üéÅ</div>
